data.title: ~*Aly & AJ*~
data.text:
- Full Name: Amanda Joy Michalka

- Birthday: April 10, 1992

- Eye color: green (trust me, they are)

- Sister of Alyson Michalka, who also goes by Aly.

- Aly & AJ sung a duet called "Do you Believe In Magic" for Aly's DCOM called "Now You See It".

- Amanda's nickname is A.J. which stands for Amanda Joy!

- Michalka is a German name and is pronounced "Mishalka".

- Aly and Aj use over 20 guitars!

- Aj has been playing the piano for 7 years and the guitar for 3 years. - Aj's hair is naturally wavy!

- Amanda and Alyson performed their own concert on Disney.

- Amanda beat Aly in ping pong during Disney's Totally Suite New Year's Eve party.

-Aly and AJ's Japanese Album was released on February 8th, 2006!

- Amanda loves to go to Mtv.com and imdb.com

- AJ has a guitar named 'Zippity' and 'Matty'.

- She and her sister love to shop on Melrose Avenue in L.A.

- Aly and AJ confirmed that actually DO check their fanmail themselves.

- Aly and Aj's debut album 'Into the Rush' has sold over 800,000 units since its release on August 16, 2005.

- Aly and Aj's first single, 'Do You Believe in Magic?', has sold over 50,000 units since release in 2004.

- Aly and AJ appear in a new commercial for VideoNow.

- Alyson claims that she is a very neat person. She likes to have things organized.

- Amanda believes that her older sister Alyson is more like a younger sister to her.

- Aly and AJ starred in their own concert on Disney.

-Favorite movies are any "Lord of the Ring" movies

- AJ shops a lot at Urban Outfitters.
